Ref: When the logical ID of this resource is provided to the Ref intrinsic function, Ref returns the resource name, such as mystack-abc1d2efg3h4. For more information about using the Ref function, see Ref.

GetAtt.Description: A list of the ingestion endpoints for the pipeline that you can send data to. Currently, only a single ingestion endpoint is supported for a pipeline. For example, my-pipeline-123456789012.us-east-1.osis.amazonaws.com.
The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the pipeline.
The VPC interface endpoints that have access to the pipeline.
The VPC endpoint service name for the pipeline.
